{
  "script_id": "prime-counting",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "素数是只能被 1 和自身整除的数，它们像质数世界的原子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.54,
      "size": 24624,
      "text": "可越往大处走，素数就越来越稀疏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "一百以内有二十五个素数，可到了一千,平均每七个数才有一个素数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "pi",
      "line_id": "pi-1",
      "filename": "pi-pi-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/pi-pi-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "我们用 π(x) 表示不超过 x 的素数个数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "pi",
      "line_id": "pi-2",
      "filename": "pi-pi-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/pi-pi-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.57,
      "size": 41184,
      "text": "每遇到一个新素数，π(x) 就往上跳一格，画出来是一条阶梯曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "pi",
      "line_id": "pi-3",
      "filename": "pi-pi-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/pi-pi-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "阶梯看似杂乱，但放到大尺度上，它竟隐藏着惊人的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "pnt",
      "line_id": "pnt-1",
      "filename": "pnt-pnt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/pnt-pnt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.78,
      "size": 44496,
      "text": "素数定理说：当 x 很大时，π(x) 约等于 x 除以 x 的自然对数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "pnt",
      "line_id": "pnt-2",
      "filename": "pnt-pnt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/pnt-pnt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "size": 49536,
      "text": "也就是 π(x) 与 x/ln(x) 的比值,会随 x 增大而越来越接近 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "pnt",
      "line_id": "pnt-3",
      "filename": "pnt-pnt-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/pnt-pnt-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "杂乱的素数，宏观上服从一条平滑而确定的曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "li",
      "line_id": "li-1",
      "filename": "li-li-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/li-li-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.72,
      "size": 43488,
      "text": "想更精确，可以用对数积分 Li(x)，也就是把 1 除以 ln t 从 2 积到 x。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "li",
      "line_id": "li-2",
      "filename": "li-li-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/li-li-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "Li(x) 几乎贴着阶梯曲线走，比 x/ln(x) 精确得多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "调整上界 x，看阶梯曲线与两条近似曲线如何越靠越紧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "x 越大，三条线几乎重合，逼近的力量一目了然。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "π(x) 数出素数个数，是一条向上的阶梯。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.67,
      "size": 42768,
      "text": "素数定理让它趋近 x/ln(x)，对数积分 Li(x) 则更精确。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "prime-counting",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/prime-counting/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "看似随机的素数，藏着深刻的秩序，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
